Package pl.edu.agh.kis.pz1

package pl.edu.agh.kis.pz1
  • Classes
    Class
    Description
    ChronologicalLogger
    The ChronologicalLogger class provides a centralized logging mechanism that maintains a chronological queue of log records.
    Library
    Library class represents shared resource where multiple threads (readers and writers) interact.
    LoggingThread
    The LoggingThread class is responsible for processing log records from the ChronologicalLogger's log queue.
    Main
    The Main class serves as the entry point for the Readers-Writers simulation.
    Reader
    The Reader class represents a reader thread that interacts with the Library.
    Writer
    The Writer class represents a writer thread.
